type: text
title: Converting Java Resource Packs To Bedrock
color: links

---

There are various ways of converting resourcepacks, please use one of the methods below:
- **Packs for 1.21.3 and below:** Run `!!oldrpconvert`
- **Packs for 1.21.4 and above:** Run `!!newrpconvert`
- **Custom GUIs on Bedrock:** Run `!!customgui`